  "remarks": "Andrei Leonidovich Kostin is the president-chairman of Vneshtorbank (VTB) – one of the leading state-owned banks in Russia. He has been the chairman of the Board of Directors of the United Shipbuilding Corporation since 25 August 2023 and is a member of the Supreme Council of the “United Russia” political party.",
